divs: Sighting DetailsI WAS SITTING OUTSIDE FACING EAST. TWO SMALL ROUND OBJECTS APPEARED FLYING EAST TO WEST, ONE ABOVE AND AHEAD OF THE OTHER. POSITIONED APPROXIMATELY MIDWAY BETWEEN JENSEN BEACH AND STUART FLORIDA.THEY WERE LOW FLYING ABOUT THE SAME AS A SMALL NEWS HELICOPTER. I STOOD UP WATCHING WONDERING WHY THERE WAS NO SOUND. THE LOWER ONE DESCENDED OUT OF SITE AND THE UPPER ONE FLEW WEST OUT OF SITE. THEY WERE FLYING ABOUT THE SPEED AS A NORMAL HELICOPTER. 12 TO 14 SECONDS DURATION. NOTHING I HAVE EVER WITNESSED. THE LACK OF NOISE IS DISTURBING.
Summary: TWO WHITE/YELLOW SPHERES FLEW LOW, 800'-1000', EAST TO WEST. NO NOISE. LOWER ONE DROPPED OUT OF SIGHT TOWARD THE GROUND.
